Package: unity-qt-launcher
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, unity-asset-pool
Description: Unity Qt Launcher
 The Unity Qt launcher displays a list of running applications as well as a
 list of favorite applications in a panel at the left of the screen.

Package: unity-qt-panel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Unity Qt Panel
 The Unity Qt panel displays a top panel containing the application menu and
 various indicators.

Package: libuqpanel0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Unity Qt Panel - shared library
 This library is used to create panel applets for the Unity Qt panel.

Package: libuqpanel-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libuqpanel0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Unity Qt Panel - development files
 This library is used to create panel applets for the Unity Qt panel.
 .
 This package contains the development header files.

Package: unity-qt-places
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, unity-qt-launcher, unity-place-files, unity-place-applications
Description: Unity Qt Places
 The Unity Qt places overlay over the desktop to provide quick access to
 various categories of applications.

